'''Classical Ossan''' was a language derived from the language of [[Ossus/Legends|Ossus]] from before its [[Battle of Ossus (Great Sith War)|destruction]] during the [[Great Sith War/Legends|Great Sith War]].

One of the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[Unidentified Jedi book|books]] was written in this language.<ref name="EE2" />

